OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall to get 55 new
OL,4,CPolice Community Support Officers
OL,6,FDevon and Cornwall is to get 55 more
OL,7,FPolice Community Support Officers
OL,8,Fafter receiving a #4.7m grant from the
OL,9,FHome Office.
OL,11,FThe money will also fund ten Special
OL,12,FConstable volunteers, while 45 police
OL,13,Fofficers will be move into
OL,14,Fneighbourbood policing roles.
OL,16,FAlison Hernandez, Police and Crime
OL,17,FCommissioner for Devon, Cornwall and
OL,18,Fthe Isles of Scilly, said the funding
OL,19,Fwas "fantastic news".
