OL,6,FShe said: "One of the things I hear
OL,7,Fmost from residents and businesses,
OL,8,Fwhether when out and about engaging
OL,9,Fwith the public, through contact with
OL,10,Fmy office, or via my regular surveys,
OL,11,Fis that they want to see more police
OL,12,Fofficers on the streets.
