OL,3,CDevon and Cornwall to get 55 new
OL,4,CPolice Community Support Officers
OL,6,F"That's why this funding is such
OL,7,Ffantastic news for the people living
OL,8,Fand working in our two counties.
OL,9,FIncreased, visible policing is proven
OL,10,Fto improve confidence and reduce
OL,11,Fcrime, as has been shown by the
OL,12,Fsuccessful hotspot policing initiative
OL,13,Fwhich has delivered excellent results
OL,14,Facross Devon and Cornwall over the
OL,15,Fpast year."
OL,17,FThe funding forms part of the
OL,18,FGovernment's Neighbourhood Policing
OL,19,FGuarantee, with #200 million available
OL,20,Fto police forces nationally in 2025/26.
