OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Glen Mayhew
OL,7,Fsaid: "Neighbourhood policing is at
OL,8,Fthe centre of how we support our
OL,9,Fcommunities. This is an additional
OL,10,Fincrease in our neighbourhood policing
OL,11,Fteams on top of the investment made by
OL,12,Fthe force last year.
OL,14,F"This is an exciting opportunity
OL,15,Fenabling us to deliver more police
OL,16,Fofficers and PCSOs into our local
OL,17,Fcommunity activity.
